'''树舌灵芝'''（{{lang-en|Ganoderma applanatum}}）<ref name="The Artist's Conk">{{cite web|last1=Overson|first1=Alissa|title=Ganoderma applanatum: The Artist's Conk|url=http://blogs.evergreen.edu/fungalkingdom/ganoderma-applanatum-the-artists-conk/|website=The Fungal Kingdom|publisher=Evergreen State College|accessdate=3 March 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112034350/http://blogs.evergreen.edu/fungalkingdom/ganoderma-applanatum-the-artists-conk/|archive-date=2015-01-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，俗稱'''老牛肝'''，是一个具有{{le|凡存种|Cosmopolitan distribution|世界性分布}}的{{le|支架真菌|Bracket fungus}}。

整个孢子体可高达30-40厘米（12-16英寸），质硬，木质纹理，和不能食用;它们是一开始是白色，但很快就变成深红褐色。棕色孢子从子实体的下侧的气孔释放出来。子实体是多年生植物，可能持续多年，尺寸在增加，气孔形成新层。

它是一种{{le|木材腐朽真菌|wood-decay fungus}}，主要利用死[[木材|木材]]，也可作为活树木的[[病原体|病原体]]，特别是在较老的树木。它是[[山毛榉|山毛榉]]和[[杨树|杨树]]腐朽和死亡的常见原因，并是对其他几个树属腐朽和死亡的较少经常的原因，包括[[桤木属|桤木属]]，[[苹果属|苹果属]]，[[榆属|榆树属]]，[[七叶树属|七叶树属]]，[[槭属|槭属(枫树)]]，[[栎属|栎属(橡木)]]，{{le|胡桃木|walnut}}，[[柳树|柳树]]，{{le|西部铁杉|western hemlock}}，[[花旗松|花旗松]]，和[[云杉属|云杉属]]。

这种真菌的特点在于它是作为艺术家的绘画介质的能力。当其表面被用锋利的工具摩擦或刮花，它从浅色变为暗褐色，产生可见的线条和阴影。

==医用==
树舌灵芝（Ganoderma applanatum）在日本被称为kofuki-saru-no-koshikake（コフキサルノコシカケ）<ref>{{cite web|title=kofuki- saru-no-koshikake (コフキサルノコシカケ)|url=http://mikawanoyasou.org/kinoko/kohukisarunokosikake.htm|website=Flora of Mikawa|accessdate=3 March 2016|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030093616/https://mikawanoyasou.org/kinoko/kohukisarunokosikake.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Mizuno|first1=Takashi|title=Sarunokoshikake: Polyporaecea fungi‐kofukisarunokoshikake, ganoderma applanatum and tsugasarunokoshikake, fomitopsis pinicola|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/87559129509541023?journalCode=lfri20|website=Taylor & Francis Online}}</ref>，字面意思是“粉覆盖猴子的长椅”，而在中国，被称为树舌灵芝，长期以来一直用于传统药物<ref name="http://asiancancerherb.info/">{{cite web|title=About Asian Anti-Cancer Materia Database|url=http://www.asiancancerherb.info/Shu%20She.htm|website=http://asiancancerherb.info/|access-date=2017-07-01|archive-date=2018-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102131203/http://asiancancerherb.info/Shu%20She.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。研究表明，灵芝包含具有有效抗肿瘤作用的化合物<ref>{{cite web|last1=MIZUNO|first1=TAKASHI|title=Isolation and characterization of antitumor active β-d-glucans from the fruit bodies of Ganoderma applanatum|url=http://thirdworld.nl/isolation-and-characterization-of-antitumor-active-b-d-glucans-from-the-fruit-bodies-of-ganoderma-applanatum|publisher=Elsevier Science Publishers B.V., Amsterdam - Printed in The Netherlands|accessdate=3 March 2016|display-authors=etal|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308033701/http://thirdworld.nl/isolation-and-characterization-of-antitumor-active-b-d-glucans-from-the-fruit-bodies-of-ganoderma-applanatum|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Antitumor Activity of Ganoderma applanatum">{{cite web|last1=Taichi Usui et. al|title=Antitumor Activity of Water-Soluble β-D-Glucan Elaborated by Ganoderma applanatum|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.1080/00021369.1981.10864512|publisher=Taylor & Francis Online|accessdate=5 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Applanoxidic acids A, B, C and D, biologically active tetracyclic triterpenes from Ganoderma applanatum|journal=Phytochemistry|date=26 March 1991|volume=30|issue=12, 1991|pages=4105–4109|doi=10.1016/0031-9422(91)83476-2|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0031942291834762|access-date=2017-07-01|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510133621/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0031942291834762|dead-url=no}}</ref>，抗细菌<ref name="Antibacterial Activity">{{cite journal|title=Antibacterial Activity of Steroidal Compounds Isolated from Ganoderma applanatum|journal=International Journal of Medicinal Mushrooms|volume=1, 1999 Issue 4|pages=325–330|doi=10.1615/IntJMedMushr.v1.i4.40|url=http://www.dl.begellhouse.com/journals/708ae68d64b17c52,541026cc01c467e3,56d7118b651c7a14.html|access-date=2017-07-01|archive-date=2020-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207003344/http://www.dl.begellhouse.com/journals/708ae68d64b17c52,541026cc01c467e3,56d7118b651c7a14.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="antibacterial properties">{{cite journal|title=Exopolysaccharide from Ganoderma applanatum as a Promising Bioactive Compound with Cytostatic and Antibacterial Properties|journal=BioMed Research International|date=July 2014|doi=10.1155/2014/743812|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/264166801_Exopolysaccharide_from_Ganoderma_applanatum_as_a_Promising_Bioactive_Compound_with_Cytostatic_and_Antibacterial_Properties|volume=2014|pages=1–10|access-date=2017-07-01|archive-date=2020-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106081133/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/264166801_Exopolysaccharide_from_Ganoderma_applanatum_as_a_Promising_Bioactive_Compound_with_Cytostatic_and_Antibacterial_Properties|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和抗纤维化<ref name="antifibrotic">{{cite journal|title=Applanatumin A, a new dimeric meroterpenoid from Ganoderma applanatum that displays potent antifibrotic activity|date=February 23, 2015|doi=10.1021/ol503610b|pmid=25706347|volume=17|journal=Org. Lett.|pages=1110–3 | last1 = Luo | first1 = Q | last2 = Di | first2 = L | last3 = Dai | first3 = WF | last4 = Lu | first4 = Q | last5 = Yan | first5 = YM | last6 = Yang | first6 = ZL | last7 = Li | first7 = RT | last8 = Cheng | first8 = YX}}</ref>的性质。

